00:28:56,890 --> 00:29:01,370
 I started to draw without realizing. 

256
00:29:01,370 --> 00:29:04,490
Why... did you acknowledge the murder?

257
00:29:04,490 --> 00:29:11,000
Because I realized that murder can give me freedom.

258
00:29:16,510 --> 00:29:19,940
No one in the world is born a murderer.

259
00:29:19,940 --> 00:29:23,340
Freedom? Back then you were scared.

260
00:29:23,340 --> 00:29:26,390
