262
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:38,680
A younger brother who put detergent in your drink, a father who didn't believe that his son was not a murderer.

263
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:41,960
And your mom, was she different?

264
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:49,180
Out of your family members, no one else came to see you other than your brother who tried to feed you detergent.

265
00:29:53,190 --> 00:29:55,980
Do you want to become family?

266
00:29:55,980 --> 00:29:56,990
Family?

267
00:29:56,990 --> 00:29:59,970
Someone who takes your side and tells you off.

268
00:29:59,970 --> 00:30:03,850
If I'm your family, then my uncles will be, too.

269
00:30:05,140 --> 00:30:11,070
I'm an ex-convict too, so I guess we are family.

270
00:30:11,070 --> 00:30:15,050
So let's have a drink to celebrate becoming a family.

271
00:30:17,870 --> 00:30:19,550
Sit down.

272
00:30:25,500 --> 00:30:27,220
Here.

273
00:30:45,360 --> 00:30:48,980
I read Romeo and Juliet many times.

274
00:30:49,910 --> 00:30:56,050
After Juliet died, why Romeo killed himself...

275
00:30:57,570 --> 00:31:03,500
Why Juliet killed herself after seeing Romeo who died because of her...

276
00:31:03,500 --> 00:31:06,730
I realized by the time I memorized the whole book.

277
00:31:07,910 --> 00:31:14,210
I'm someone... who can never feel that.

278
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:28,280
Other people call this love.

279
00:31:29,630 --> 00:31:34,850
Your eyes become hot and your mouth becomes dry,

280
00:31:34,850 --> 00:31:37,260
and your breathing becomes faster,

281
00:31:38,890 --> 00:31:42,430
and you become soft-hearted.

282
00:31:42,430 --> 00:31:45,640
You're this close to me...

283
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:47,100
♫   This heart of mine   ♫

284
00:31:47,100 --> 00:31:53,870
...but I'm scared when you might disappear.

285
00:31:56,760 --> 00:32:05,340
♫   The way that you look sad sometimes   ♫

286
00:32:05,340 --> 00:32:07,990
♫   I tried to pretend not to know   ♫

287
00:32:07,990 --> 00:32:11,420
Not family...

288
00:32:11,420 --> 00:32:14,730
Please be my woman.

289
00:32:14,730 --> 00:32:18,190
♫   I wonder if you'll get to know my heart   ♫

290
00:32:19,130 --> 00:32:25,000
♫   Even though I know you can't come to me   ♫

